    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick a theme and craft your own story by making branching choices that shape each unique adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You'll be able to explore distinct themes, each offering a unique scenario: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on a seven-year journey at a magic school, where you'll master your powers and unravel ancient mysteries </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lead a party of heroes on a rescue mission to save a lost prince</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Establish and fortify an outpost in newly conquered territory, ensuring the prosperity and security of your ancient empire’s expansion</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Including a variety of unique themes and situations to start your journey from</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Customize characters looks, abilities and backstories</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Guide your story with meaningful choices that mold your characters and their world</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Intuitive controls, game-play and interactions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Cute 3D art-style</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Discover secret and hidden elements to personalize your creations</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Be careful, as you shape your creations, they shape <strong>you</strong></p></li></ul>",
